    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Tests the effects of exceptional values (e.g., inf, nan) on the vertex fog coordinate. Fog is set to bright red.</para>
<para>Each test renders a series of blueish quads with their fog coordinate set to interesting test values to observe the resulting behavior. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
